The paper proposes a convolutional neural network based image enhancement model for underwater images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also deals with image processing and graphics (cs.GR), multimedia (cs.MM), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG) which are all relevant sub-categories.
